casesfig.name: Total COVID-19 Cases
casesfig.definition: is the number of people who have tested positive for COVID-19 in each county.

deathsfig.name: Total COVID-19 Deaths
deathsfig.definition: is the number of people who have died of confirmed or presumed COVID-19 cases in each county.

dailycases.name: Daily COVID-19 Cases
dailycases.definition: is the new number of cases as of the date the data is updated.

dailydeaths.name: Daily COVID-19 Deaths
dailydeaths.definition: is the new number of deaths as of the date the data is updated.

mean7daycases.name: Average Daily COVID-19 Cases
mean7daycases.definition: is the average number of positive cases for COVID-19 infection per county in the United States over the last seven days.

mean7daydeaths.name: Average Daily COVID-19 Deaths
mean7daydeaths.definition: is the average number of deaths due to confirmed or presumed COVID-19 infection per county in the United States over the last seven days.

caseratefig.name: Total COVID-19 Cases per 100,000
caseratefig.definition: helps us understand COVID-19 cases (people who have tested positive for COVID-19) by the population of the county per 100,000 people.

covidmortalityfig.name: Total COVID-19 Deaths per 100,000
covidmortalityfig.definition: helps us understand COVID-19 deaths by population of the county per 100,000 people.

caserate7dayfig.name: Average Daily COVID-19 Cases per 100,000
caserate7dayfig.definition: helps us understand the average number of positive cases for COVID-19 infection over the last seven days by population of the county per 100,000 people.

covidmortality7dayfig.name: Average Daily COVID-19 Deaths per 100,000
covidmortality7dayfig.definition: helps us understand the average number of deaths due to confirmed or presumed COVID-19 infection over the last seven days by population of the county per 100,000 people.
